content: I'm trying to plan my meals for the next week and I was wondering if you could suggest some recipes that use chicken breast. I've been buying it in bulk lately and I want to use it up before it expires. By the way, I've been trying to reduce my grocery spending, and I'm glad I stocked up on some staples last week at Walmart - it really helped. Speaking of which, I had a fun trip to Trader Joe's the week before that with my sister and we spent around $80 between the two of us.
